data.description: **LARGE PRICE REDUCTION**MOTIVATED SELLER.  Subject Home + Bonus Lot Sold Together!!!  Rare opportunity to own a beautiful 3 Bed, 2 Bath home with an extra residential lot in the quickly growing community of Menifee!  The Bonus parcel of land could provide the buyer with options for future development or expansion. The property offers ample  space, for recreational vehicles (RVs), boats, as well as the potential for future additional structures like an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU). Sewer is being brought into the area by EMWD in phases, contact listing agent for more info, and clarification regarding utilities. Tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac street this home features a panoramic backyard view of Canyon Lake & rolling hills which adds a scenic and serene element. This home is not located inside the Gated community SO NO HOA! This spacious home has an oversized 2 car garage with upgraded Epoxy Floors, new tile in both spare bedrooms & master bath & comes with owned propane tank. PRE APPROVAL or DU APPROVAL must be submitted for a Showing. ALL OFFERS DUE SUNDAY 12/17/93 BY 6PM
